ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Establishment Licensing Fees (Veterinary Drugs) Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE ESTABLISHMENT LICENSING FEES (VETERINARY DRUGS) REGULATIONS in order to exempt veterinary active pharmaceutical ingredients from fees associated with the examination of an application for or the amendment of an establishment license — or the annual review of an establishment license — that deal exclusively with veterinary active pharmaceutical ingredients.
